Apple is designing an updated version of the <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/roundup/apple-tv/">Apple TV</a> 4K, and rumors suggest that it could come out sometime in the next couple of months. We're not expecting a major overhaul with design changes, but even a simple chip upgrade will bring major improvements to Apple's set-top box.<br/>
<br/>
